Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.97,0:00:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, everyone, it's May. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was so depressed because I failed last time,\Nand I was moping about it all by myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I realized something\Nafter Meryl talked to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've just been looking for excuses,\Nblaming things on somebody else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is May Wong,\Nan athlete who never gives up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.15,0:00:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will not let anybody get in my way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora, you're not the only one trying\Nto get to the place where Miss Layla is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:01:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the beginning\Nis red and black passions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.25,0:01:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes, we rely on our contrary hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the last resort is a\Nmission which changes the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.82,0:01:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no place for\Nambiguous answers in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even while pretending not to\Nsee the impossible reality, we bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hard-to-obtain-truth\NCan you feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I say to myself,\Nwho gets excited easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm confused about what to say {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' the never-waking\Ndream, the falling fate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe in you, even\Nif I lose everything for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if this is okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon said you passed, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means he's acknowledged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations for being\Nable to participate in the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you concerned about May?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but just think about the \Nfestival for right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Sora. Your goal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, say it with me, everybody:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only one of us is able to\Nparticipate in the festival.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, in order for me to participate\Nin the festival, I have to beat May.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.21,0:03:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kalos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Sora's here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The final test?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final test?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Two Amazing Demons."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have them prepare\Nfor the final test right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, if she is going to participate\Nin the festival, she can't sidestep this test.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:04:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if she missteps once,\Nher career on the stage may end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora can pull through this. I believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The final test... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can pass this, that\NPhoenix Ticket will be mine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mustn't think about May.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of test it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of\Ntest it is, she'll be okey-dokey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is cheering for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I will ask you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you seriously want to participate in\Nthe Circus Festival no matter what happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pass this test.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how difficult\Nthe maneuver is, I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no other alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Climb up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to do a layout somersault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a layout somersault?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among the trapeze maneuvers, that's\Nthe most basic among of all the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The performer spins once,\Nand grabs the catcher's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remove the safety net.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:06:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you perform in the festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have neither a safety net nor a lifeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A maneuver as basic as\Nthis should not require a net.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will create a chance for you to show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what he said to May. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will create a chance for you to show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will create a perfect chance\Nfor you to show off in today's show.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you fail the final \Ntest before you take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remove the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A good attitude, Sora. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Show me how ready you are to be a real star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll jump next time. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jump like you mean it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hesitating can be dangerous, Sora.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's perfect timing. I can do this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't jump. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe this. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I thought of what\NI'd do if he doesn't catch me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't jump. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me try one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you do it for real in the festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you going to ask me\Nto do it one more time too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Please let me try one more--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unseemly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way it is now, we'll have no\Nparticipants in this year's festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Leon Oswald must\Nwant to participate in the festival
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to wipe out his\Nshame from three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is his purpose in staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the rumor that he was looking\Nfor a partner who can match his level.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:09:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all the partners he\Nhad in the past left the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he treats them\Nall like he did May Wong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if they can leave the\Nstage over something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think they'd be better off if\Nthey quit and found another career.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing that, and he still invited Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means Leon must have thought\Nthat Sora could be his partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he thought he could win in the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, Sora is still\Ntrying to follow your footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for her to surpass Layla Hamilton,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she has no other choice\Nbut to win in the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's the starting line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you haven't given up on your wish yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.08,0:09:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you're the one who\Nwas first attracted to Sora's potential
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pressured her into appearing on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do anything if I can make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos, if you were capable of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage would never wind up in a pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was meant as a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Sora is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially after she saw \Nwhat happened to May.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should leave her alone right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I even endured that special training.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wasted everything. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I disappointed Miss Layla. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora, you're so stupid. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't have the\Nconfidence to pair with Mr. Leon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to perform even the\Nlegendary great maneuver with Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you can't even\Ndo a basic maneuver with Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.87,0:10:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A real star doesn't change her\Nshine depending on who's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that I can't be a real star?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know for sure that being a real\Nstar is something very distant for you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because of the way you're acting right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's far...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's far, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is endlessly far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that May hasn't been in\Nher room since before last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? May?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the ball, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pass, pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.98,0:11:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks kinda depressed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meryl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.28,0:12:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come here to laugh at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... May, I have something\NI want to talk to you about...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! What could you \Nhave to say to me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon chose you. You won.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more proud of your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And laugh at me, the one who lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, I won't laugh at...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the thing about \Nyou that makes me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a newcomer, I picked\Na fight with you, the top star,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and just when I was feeling like hot stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking I grabbed away\Nthe lead role away from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the end I wasn't seen as\Nanything but a tool to train you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He injured my shoulder, and I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that funny? Laugh at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh at me... at least.\NNo way do I want your sympathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're wrong, May.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't pass Leon's final test.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid of Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid of him, and I couldn't\Nrelease my hands from the swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then, the partner has not...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It hasn't been decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't come back to the dormitory,\Nso you didn't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I thought I had to tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly am I supposed to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what I should do either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what I want to say is...\Nwell, I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so hesitant!\NYou're irritating me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come all the way here to find\NMay and tell her something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you start giving up so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you act like that, you should have\Nlistened to what I said, and kept skating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything?\NYou don't know what to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, it looks like you\Njust don't want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy for you to say,\Nbut I was abandoned by Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were injured because\Nyou didn't have the skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you can't\Nhandle a little ad lib like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to blame\Nsomething, blame your lack of skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like you're the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who abandoned you is you, May!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The May I remember is:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when someone told you "no,"\Nyou used to work so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that the person would never\Nbe able to say "no" to you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never said you couldn't\Ndo something, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to my sis like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! You dumb kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyah, nyah, nyah, nyah, nyah, nyah, nyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may still have a chance too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Meryl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered how bad I am at giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll challenge Leon one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you've gotten motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I also have to thank you too, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking the time\Nand coming all the way down here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to let me know that you were disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be his {\i1}real {\i0}partner this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you afraid of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.92,0:16:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he sees my new maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Leon will grab my hands this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with that maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to participate in the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make the world acknowledge\Nme like they did Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new maneuver...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that name is: Demon Spiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Spiral... What kind \Nof maneuver is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the practice room, \NI'm going to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, I'm going back to the dormitory again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, can you tell that to Mom and Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone back to the sis we know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, she's such trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Sora, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you just stand there and watch her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't want to. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.48,0:17:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say you can't trust your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as May.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're blaming your\Nlack of skill on your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before you say this and \Nthat about your partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you doing enough to\Nearn your partner's trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be my partner the way you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reduce your part further tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of worrying about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,improve your skills so that\Nyou're good enough to satisfy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is important,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think the Kids' Stage is important too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You talk pretty, but aren't\Nyou just running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you face Layla\NHamilton with all your might?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you do the same for this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay like this,\Nyour path will stay blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who\Ncan cut your way through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.91,0:17:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true. I was facing\NMiss Layla like a daredevil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't have the confidence\Nto act the same with Mr. Leon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How on Earth can I... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, I don't like his attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you ask who else \Ncould play his role...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.14,0:18:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we want to have an eye\Non winning in the festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't Sora do it by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, the rule is\Nthat she has to be in a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch, I'll do all of his\Nmaneuvers easily in three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Rosetta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but I asked everybody to gather\Ntoday because I wanted encourage Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you encourage someone,\Ncould you please encourage Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more than thankful for\Nthe way all of you care about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of this is my own problem. Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, for Sora, I'll show \Nyou amazing martial arts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which can't even be drawn by human hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No, that's not necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.94,0:19:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. This certainly\Ncouldn't be drawn by human hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, was it helpful?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well... kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since nobody is in, the air is cool.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right, the cool space\Nwhere I'm alone is where I belong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After I joined Kaleido Stage I decided that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order for someone like me\Nwho just joined Kaleido Stage{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to bring down a top star like Sora\Neven one minute or one second faster,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could not afford to goof\Naround with those others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If they don't like me,\Nthey can just not like me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If they hate me, they can just hate me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to win by all means! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The movement that time... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because he didn't have both hands on the bar,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that's why he was able to do\Nthat kind of unexpected move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can use that move\Nand create a new maneuver...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will perfect this maneuver by all means.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no other path forward. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to surpass Miss Layla, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and also in order to be a true Kaleido Star,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to participate in the\NCircus Festival no matter what.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to! I want to!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, I still don't know what I should do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even though May already found\Nsomething and started running toward it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taurus found its way out of the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Sagittarius is\Nstill engulfed in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, if you exert yourself\Nhaphazardly, you'll just spin in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me what I'm supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here she is. Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Rosetta, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be\Nexchanging laid-back small talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May said she's going to challenge Leon again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew you'd be the one\Nto ask me for another challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this new maneuver is\Nsupposed to be able to satisfy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.42,0:21:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it will, Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who\Ncan catch my Demon Spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you screw up, I will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:22:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're the God of Death, I'll be a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.64,0:22:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Spiral is a challenge\Nfrom a devil to the God of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect you to accept my challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. This is my duel with fate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Spiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All kinds of hard luck flocks\Nyour way as if it's spurring you on{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Swept away by it, time is over {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as predicted, take it easy {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:23:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will get you out right away {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up (Here we go) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forcibly only (Drive with the fastest speed){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.14,0:23:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The view I look down at every day is the best{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sunset point (Favorite) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harbor light (Stormy night) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Escape for the sake of tomorrow {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even I don't have a vacation, \NI've got an oasis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll turn off the cell \Nphone and charge my love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because some pain,\Nyou can't soothe with just kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.21,0:23:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are alone, we pass each other by{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.85,0:23:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the far end of regret,\NI encounter my true heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.38,0:23:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether I'm crying or\Nlaughing, I will be with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:57.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star: New Wings"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:23:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I was at Kaleido Stage, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think I looked at\Nthe audience's faces much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, the Demon Spiral was amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But no, I can't back down like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.68,0:24:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being bad at giving up \Nis something I patented!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it's with him... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.38,0:24:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right! I will show them\Nwhat I'm like when I'm serious too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.64,0:24:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll show them! I'll show them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.50,0:24:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star,\N"Amazing Angelic Counterattack."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.85,0:24:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream\Nand on towards the sky...{\i0}
